Review: Riled me up, which I think was the point, but riled me up in the wrong way. Main character came off egotistical and passive. Much more interested in the characters that have to personal consequences that heighten their ethical dilemma like Alisha and Dwayne, rather than the characters that got to go home afterwards and pretend nothing happened.

Totally felt like it was inspired by the best silent movie of all time Cabinet of Dr CaligariYorgos movies mean a lot to me n my family we’ve seen…
